@@TJvPageScroller
<TITLEIMG TJvPageScroller>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.CommCtrl
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  A TPageScroller with additional events.
Description
  Use TJvPageScroller as a replacement for TPageScroller when you need access to events like OnMouseEnter,
  OnMouseLeave, OnCtl3DChanged and OnParentColorChange and properties like HintColor.
